---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Practical Car Rental Guides | TripAxle"
  description="Practical car rental guides for insurance, tolls, debit card rules, and common booking mistakes."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Practical guides</p>
    <h1>Practical car rental guides for smarter trips.</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Use these guides to understand the common details travelers miss before they
      book: insurance, tolls, debit card rules, transmission choice, and more.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="guide-grid">
    <article class="guide-card">
      <h2>Insurance Guide</h2>
      <p>
        Understand the main insurance decisions travelers face before pickup.
      </p>
      <a href="#">See insurance guide →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="guide-card">
      <h2>Toll Roads Guide</h2>
      <p>
        Learn what to check about toll systems before driving in Portugal.
      </p>
      <a href="#">See toll guide →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="guide-card">
      <h2>Debit Card Rules</h2>
      <p>
        See the most important debit card issues travelers should verify before
        reserving.
      </p>
      <a href="#">See debit card guide →</a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <article class="main-card">
      <h2>What these guides will help with</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Avoiding common misunderstandings before pickup</li>
        <li>Knowing what to verify before finalizing a booking</li>
        <li>Understanding extra costs and fine-print issues</li>
        <li>Making better platform and rental choices overall</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to use this hub</h2>
      <p>
        Start here if you already know your destination but want help with the
        practical side of renting. These pages will support the airport guides,
        booking comparisons, and country-level hubs.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-card">
      <h2>Planned practical guides</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Insurance guide</li>
        <li>Toll roads guide</li>
        <li>Debit card guide</li>
        <li>Automatic vs manual guide</li>
        <li>Deposit and hold guide</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0 2.25rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #5b5b55;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .guide-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .guide-card,
    .main-card,
    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e4e4de;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .guide-card h2,
    .main-card h2,
    .side-card h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .guide-card p {
      color: #5b5b55;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .guide-card a {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2f6fed;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .guide-grid,
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>